# Sinking Point: Dynamic Precision Tracking for Floating-point

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in `pubs/2019-conga-sinkingpoint/`.

Edit `pubs/2019-conga-sinkingpoint/publication.json` for structured publication
data, keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and use
